    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><style>[data-colorid=me25zaf38f]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=me25zaf38f]{color:#004eb3}</style></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_full.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_full.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761485850075&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=425\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_full.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761485850075&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"804\" data-width=\"1435\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632848960\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_full.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"4768d0d1-fc88-47a8-a739-6dd7c19af23f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_full.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761485850075&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=850 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_full.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761485850075&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=425 1x\" /></span><p>This lesson demonstrates how you can approach your shading layers from a storytelling perspective.  </p><p>Scratch your surfaces with purpose, why dirt is gathered in particular crevices, and how decals can add story to your props.</p><p>Each stage in this shader layering was a LamaLayer with the mix controlled by either a hand-painted or procedural mask.</p><p /><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"me25zaf38f\">Meet OTTO!</span></strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_Lama_Stage1.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1761502337790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1761502337790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632848998\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_Lama_Stage1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"7c752e64-54ee-4d6c-83a2-fa6fc4f87545\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1761502337790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage1.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1761502337790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>Once upon a time, there was a robot called OTTO who rolled off the production line all shiny and new, ready for work.  He started all nice and clean.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_Lama_Stage2.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502343785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502343785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632750611\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_Lama_Stage2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"861d984a-e562-4baa-bc5b-a89b73e44871\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502343785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502343785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>Until one day, whilst helping fix a machine, a clumsy intern spilled a can of oil all over OTTO, ruining his clean, shiny metal.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_Lama_Stage3.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502347628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502347628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632685217\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_Lama_Stage3.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"05181b1a-f726-4c7c-9085-71989a61d4d6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502347628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage3.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502347628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>OTTO, all oily and greasy, had no option but to go to the dreaded re-spray department.  No robot ever wanted to go in there, as they always took pride in their shiny metal.</p><p>OTTO had to be re-sprayed in the factory default - grey.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_Lama_Stage4.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502353680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502353680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632685223\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_Lama_Stage4.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"8c18a9d0-6074-43ef-b40d-18a54f4d3d47\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502353680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502353680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>Whilst he was waiting for his new paint to dry, some vandals broke in and decided to graffiti all over OTTO.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_Lama_Stage5.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502362833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502362833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632783426\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_Lama_Stage5.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"fa0917bd-abae-46b3-b683-e50c713044df\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502362833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502362833&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>Since OTTO was now looking far worse for wear, he was left in the corner to rust.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Robot_Lama_Stage6.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502375500&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502375500&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"632783432\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Robot_Lama_Stage6.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606175285\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"7f0e5424-4a6a-427a-84d7-2b858a6bdc80\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502375500&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606175285/Robot_Lama_Stage6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761502375500&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\" /></span><p>And over time, he got forgotten about and just stood in the corner of the factory gathering dirt and dust.</p><p /><p /><p />"
    }
